query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `carrierlockStates` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `mentalNoise` int NOT NULL,
  `bodyTension` int NOT NULL,
  `emotionalTurbulence` int NOT NULL,
  `breathCompletion` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `coherenceScore` int NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
